{"tid":211419,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"PTT停機6小時 鄉民哀號世界末日來了","createTime":"2017-04-21T15:24:50.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-21T16:15:17.000Z","uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f7c4b49a8091e1ef58770fbe9ec74052a57c16d6","tid":211419,"uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T15:24:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://pgw.udn.com.tw/gw/photo.php?u=https://uc.udn.com.tw/photo/2017/04/16/98/3405329.jpg&amp;x=0&amp;y=0&amp;sw=0&amp;sh=0&amp;sl=W&amp;fw=1050&amp;exp=3600\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpgw.udn.com.tw%2Fgw%2Fphoto.php%3Fu%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fuc.udn.com.tw%2Fphoto%2F2017%2F04%2F16%2F98%2F3405329.jpg%26x%3D0%26y%3D0%26sw%3D0%26sh%3D0%26sl%3DW%26fw%3D1050%26exp%3D3600&h=f276ddde&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n國內知名BBS社群平台PTT因配合高壓配電設備維修，從下午五時至晚上十一時停機6小時，公告在13日發布後，許多鄉民大喊崩潰，哀號世界末日要來了，停機前還依依不捨，相約6小時後見。<br />\n<br />\nPTT(批踢踢)在13日晚間貼出停機公告指出，16日配合高壓配電設備緊急維修，PTT、PTT2、PTT網頁板於下午五時至晚上十一時暫停服務。<br />\n<br />\n公告一貼出後，鄉民大喊崩潰，噓聲四起，有人說「暴動囉」、「又到了試吃芥末的日子了！」、 「人生失去意義」、「突然失去夢想」。<br />\n<br />\n停機前幾分鐘更是湧入大量的發文和推文，有人問卦「大家六小時後會上來衝紫爆嗎？」、「肥宅什麼時候能再相逢」、「關機後的城武們該怎麼辦？」、「搶到關機前的最後推文，發P幣」，鄉民們依依不捨，相約6小時後見。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://udn.com/news/story/7266/2406799\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fudn.com%2Fnews%2Fstory%2F7266%2F2406799&d=Se3jk6qONbDe%2BTgec%2FNeB1zEg0sy7MJ6GkP0ogsbSqo%3D&h=a8b8763d\" target=\"_blank\">https://udn.com/news/story/7266/2406799</a>"},{"pid":"8c1e25dadfd63fdbc3138ff4a0987aa620c1474e","tid":211419,"uid":51720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T15:26:37.000Z","msg":"本港都熄過登 N 次啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9f5c3dd6b320957ac742ed0faea74bae5fea21a","tid":211419,"uid":75694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T15:36:51.000Z","msg":"開返個LiPTT <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 以防死server 用"},{"pid":"dd08219d44e4fd